column5: I need to contact the office for Midwest USA. Thanks
I'm confused..you're looking for an Immigration Canada office in the US?

[font color=green size=3][b]The Canadian Citezenship and Immigration number in Fort Francis is 807-274-3815 or if it's busy, 807-274-3818, also 1-888-242-2100, but that one might not work from the US, a lot of Canadian 800 & 888 numbers don't.
